      <div class="dp-cover-eyebrow">bearerCORE™ · System Design &amp; UI Behavior Specification</div>
      <h1>Audit &amp; Reports — Forensic Workstation</h1>
      <p class="dp-cover-desc">
        Complete backend and frontend specification for the Audit &amp; Reports tab. Implements a
